.TH LOOTSHEET-JOURNAL-REVERSE 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-journal-reverse \\- Reverse a posted journal entry
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet journal reverse [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet journal reverse --entry-id UUID --date YYYY-MM-DD [--description TEXT]

Examples:
  lootsheet journal reverse --entry-id abc-123 --date 2026-03-09
  lootsheet journal reverse --entry-id abc-123 --date 2026-03-09 --description "Correcting duplicate entry"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--date=string
reversal date in YYYY-MM-DD (default: )
.TP
--description=string
optional reversal description (default: )
.TP
--entry-id=string
UUID of the journal entry to reverse (default: )
.TP
-h, --help
help for reverse
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-journal(1)
